_mkfs_ - make a new file system

_mkfs_ [-*pv*] [-s *blocks*] *dev* [*bitmap* [*dir*]]

 -*p*   preserve owner and group when populating the fs
 -*v*   verbose operation

 *dev*     device name to make the fs on
 *blocks*  fs size in blocks
 *bitmap*  free block bitmap offset (default 2)
 *dir*     source directory to populate the new fs with
